Comment: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:50.06,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H0F0F0F&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\fs21}簡單地說就是…主人遭遇危機了！
Comment: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:50.06,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H0F0F0F&\3c&HFFFFFF&\an7\fs21}還要看哦！
